name: Sweventel • The Hand of Nox
description: The hand of the sovereign succubus reaches forth from the vortex of the crossworld eclipse to cast her magic, in this uninvited nightmarish visitation. The halls of histories and futures tell the tales of doom and deliverance in the times of the eschaton. Entities of the cosmic mind, entoptic symbols, pareidolia, spells and enchantments emerge from the chambers of the subconscious to become reality. Image size: 12,000 x 8,000 pixels.
